globulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, More', 'Fluphenazine, Thiothixene, Amisulpride, Promazine, Thioridazine, Trifluoperazine, Paliperidone, Chlorpromazine, Mesoridazine, Methotrimeprazine, Clozapine, More', 1767369485);
